> ls -l     long listing

drwxr-xr-x 2 staxx6 staxx6 4096 2. Okt 17:06 NAME
T||||||||| H owner  group  size date   time  name
 usr||||||
    grp|||
       oth

# Type:
 -          normal
 d          directory
 b or c     device-data (block or char)
 l          symbolic link
 s          socket
 p          pipe

# Permission:
r   read
w   write
x   execute
-   nothing

# Hardlink:

### ls
> ls -lR            long list and recursive (-r is reverse order!)
> ls -lR | less     good help